{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Advocate confiscation & dismantling of any undisclosed Israeli nuclear weapons",
        "additional_details": "The UK should lead the effort to support nuclear non-proliferation consistently. Undeclared nuclear weapons risk undermining global security and trust in international relations. By raising this issue through the United Nations, the UK could drive efforts to promote transparency and equal enforcement of nuclear regulations in order to strengthen global security and help reduce the risk of conflict.",
        "background": "We call on the UK Government to support in the confiscation and dismantling of any undisclosed Israeli nuclear weapons. The UK Government should drive this effort through the United Nations to ensure that no state operates outside of international nuclear regulations.",
